comments: Dunn (UTA) and Sabonis (SAC) briefly engage and disengage as the pick is set.
Sabonis (SAC) briefly grasps Agbaji's (UTA) arm and marginal contact occurs as they disengage following the pick.
Dunn (UTA) contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs after Fox has released his jump shot.
Fox (SAC) brings his arm toward Dunn's (UTA) front and marginal contact occurs as Dunn is passing the ball.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Agbaji's (UTA) path and does not deliver contact.
Kessler's (UTA) right hand makes clean contact with the ball and the ensuing contact with Sabonis (SAC) as he gathers the entry pass is marginal.
Kessler (UTA) makes contact with the ball as he defends Sabonis' (SAC) shot near the rim.  Any ensuing contact with Sabonis' arm/wrist is considered incidental.
Kessler (UTA) brings his hands toward Fox (SAC) and marginal contact occurs as Kessler releases away to roll to the basket.
Fox (SAC) swipes his arm down and initiates contact with Dunn's (UTA) lower body that affects Dunn's SQBR.
Sabonis (SAC) is already in Agbaji's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Kessler (UTA) is retreating his arm into a vertical position and marginal contact occurs with Sabonis (SAC) during his shot near the rim.
Monk (SAC) moves laterally into Dunn's (UTA) path and initiates lower body contact that affects Dunn's SQBR.
Fox (SAC) moves laterally into Agbaji's (UTA) path and initiates contact as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Agbaji's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis releases away to roll towards the basket.
Olynyk (UTA) legally contests Barnes' (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Fontecchio (UTA) and Murray (SAC) briefly engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Murray (SAC) and Fontecchio (UTA) come together at the same spot and Murray cleanly deflects the ball as Fontecchio attempts to pass.
Fox (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Kessler (UTA) as they pursue the rebound.
Barnes (SAC) makes contact with Kessler's (UTA) arm that causes Kessler to lose control of the ball.
Murray (SAC) is already in Dunn's (UTA) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage during the inbound.
Murray (SAC) establishes himself in Fontecchio's (UTA) path and does not deliver contact.
Dunn (UTA) contests Monk's (SAC) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) briefly grasps Kessler's (UTA) arm and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Barnes (SAC) commits a take foul on Olynyk (UTA).
